  <div class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-terminal-text/80 space-y-4 font-sans max-w-xl">
    <p>I'm Nick Yeager. I'm an AI Solutions Architect based in Tucson, Arizona.</p>

    <p>I've spent 15+ years building software across healthcare, finance, insurance, and startups. Most recently I was Lead Engineer at ScriptSave, where I built an industry-first AI pharmaceutical assistant. Before that I shipped code at Alicat Scientific, USAA, and a handful of startups — including one I co-founded.</p>

    <p>These days I consult on AI strategy and implementation, and give talks about what it actually takes to ship AI products. Less hype, more reality.</p>

    <p>I have a BA in Political Science from the University of Arizona. I also coach pickleball.</p>
